data.description: 5 Bed/Bonus Rooms + Full Daylight Basement in Northgate HS area! Master on Main! Over $100,000 in Upgrades! And Over 4,000 sq ft including finished basement.  Upgrades: Brand New Roof, 40k in ALL NEW Low-E Windows, New Interior & Exterior Paint, New garage door opener, New Stainless Steel Black Appliances, Finished Basement with HVAC, Electrical and New Flooring, Granite in Kitchen, Updated Master Bath with dual granite vanity, new Shower, tile and toilet. Updated kitchen cabinets, new light fixtures and fans. Renovated deck.  Home has Master on Main, Bath with dual granite vanity, with separate tub & new shower. 2-story Foyer to Living Room open to Kitchen, Dining Room, Breakfast Room or Sun Room, Laundry and Powder Room. Full finished basement, open layout with new flooring and paint, leads to workshop with boat door. Upstairs 4 Bedrooms/Bonus Rooms, extra large bedroom could be media room. Full Bathroom plus, extra Vanity/sink room! Huge Deck overlooks green space and winter lake view with fenced yard under deck. Only 3 houses down from the path to Lake Judy for fishing and sunsets. Terrific Coweta Northgate Schools, and new Blake Bass Middle School. Just down from new Publix at Arbor Springs.  Easy access to I-85, Airport, Newnan, Tyrone, Chick-fil-A HQ, Peachtree City and Trilith. Option to Join nearby Canongate Golf Club for Golf or just Social Membership POOL, Tennis, 1/2 price Dining and Events.
